to update a new hcana branch (update-april2020)
1)build hcana as an usual way with the develop branch and make sure origin(you) and remote(jlab) is good.
2)Follow ROOT analyzer git and do scons-j8, and you should not see any errors
3)git checkout develop
4)git pull upstream develop  
This will update develop branch
5)to switch to new branch ( update-april2020)
git checkout -b update-april2020
6)to make it even with jlab 
git pull upstream update-april2020 
